        {
            "title": "HashKey據悉最快下周接受香港IPO認購 擬籌集至少2億美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"HashKey據悉最快下周接受香港IPO認購 擬籌集至少2億美元\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"637\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/KDtFVSe_0zL4HQpts7bZqw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzNztjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-10/f1bb9460-a642-11f0-bcf9-20b469dc1877\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">HashKey據悉最快下周接受香港IPO認購 擬籌集至少2億美元</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
