        {
            "title": "荷蘭養老金系統改革影響深遠 歐洲國家或因此縮短舉債期限",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 隨著荷蘭養老金系統的改革導致對較長期債券的需求減少，歐洲國家考慮縮短舉債期限。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著各國政府公佈2026年債券發行計畫，相關的調整可能在未來幾周內宣布。奧地利債務主管本周表示，在持續多年聚焦較長期債券後，該國的債務平均期限「有下行空間」，成為預示未來趨勢的初步信號。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐元區若採用較短期的融資策略，將會效仿英國和日本的做法。由於投資者對持有較長期債券要求更高的回報，上述變化也可能降低政府的利息支付，但由於因此需要更加頻繁地為到期債務再融資，也會令其更容易受到殖利率上升的衝擊。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-83fb5780-0449-3300-a63c-7cbe44715795-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tKgc9Oiolhl3_UeQ8j91aw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/6d750f2f04075041cfe3840c24bd6b1b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上述潛在的變化源於荷蘭養老基金將在未來兩年內轉向固定繳款模式，這意味著其對超長期債券的購買量可能下降，因其不再需要實現資產與負債的匹配。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管荷蘭僅占歐元區經濟總量的7%，但其養老金體系卻是舉足輕重的市場參與者。據歐洲央行數據顯示，荷蘭養老金持有的主權債在整個地區養老金機構的此類持倉中占比約達65%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Dutch Pension Overhaul to Fuel Pivot From Long Bonds in EU (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Patrick Van Oosterom、James Hirai.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8D%B7%E8%98%AD%E9%A4%8A%E8%80%81%E9%87%91%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E6%B7%B1%E9%81%A0-%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E6%88%96%E5%9B%A0%E6%AD%A4%E7%B8%AE%E7%9F%AD%E8%88%89%E5%82%B5%E6%9C%9F%E9%99%90-113007024.html",
